@abdosi  Hi Abhishek,  In order to allow  build pass with the new change of the init_cfg.json.j2 file,  I think we need to modify the following three files:
	src/sonic-yang-models/tests/files/sample_config_db.json
        src/sonic-yang-models/tests/yang_model_tests/tests_config/feature.json
	src/sonic-yang-models/yang-models/sonic-feature.yang
The following is the patch, please check it if they are needed.
```
